}

' Relationships
MacOSChangeWatcher ..|> ChangeWatcher : implements
MacOSChangeWatcher *-- FSEventsMonitor : contains
MacOSChangeWatcher *-- FileProviderIntegration : contains
MacOSChangeWatcher *-- MacOSPlatformInfo : creates
MacOSChangeWatcher ..> FileOperation : uses

FSEventsMonitor ..> FSEventCallback : uses
FSEventsMonitor ..> FSEvent : creates
FSEventsMonitor ..> CFRunLoop : uses
FSEventsMonitor --> "FSEventStreamCreate" : uses

FileProviderIntegration ..> FileProviderCallback : uses
FileProviderIntegration ..> NSFileProviderRequest : handles
FileProviderIntegration ..> NSFileProviderItem : manages
FileProviderIntegration --> "NSFileProvider" : uses

FSEvent ..> FileOperation : represents
NSFileProviderRequest ..> ProviderRequestType : has

' Notes
note top of MacOSChangeWatcher : Main integration point\nfor macOS platform.\nUses native APIs

note right of FSEventsMonitor : Low-level monitoring\nthrough macOS FSEvents API.\nRuns in separate thread

note bottom of FileProviderIntegration : Integration with Finder through\nFile Provider Framework.\nSupports virtual filesystem

note left of MacOSPlatformInfo : Information about macOS\nplatform capabilities.\nReturns true for FSEvents

@enduml
